Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Reside at historic Thomas Park, where history and modern elegance intersect. This newly constructed townhouse style home offers two personal entrances, deeded off-street parking and a wonderful private yard facing Thomas Park. As you enter what was once the horse stable, you will be greeted by a remarkable chef's kitchen that overlooks a spacious living area with soaring ceilings. The kitchen includes Thermador appliances, quartz counters, custom cabinets and great space for storage. Upstairs, you'll find what was previously a hayloft, now a sunny loft-style bonus room that offers versatility in your floor plan. The lower level reveals three bedrooms, two spa-like bathrooms, and in-unit laundry. Central air and a smart BLINK system ensure comfort and security. Located in a highly walkable area, 75 G is a collection of three distinctive residences that have been thoughtfully designed to preserve the charm of a historical home while offering the advantages of new construction.
